How can you pay homage to such a talented performer in a brief précis?
Tonight Laura Morera has her very last dance at the ROH as Anastasia. She has been there for 27 years, and was a brilliant female principal. She is sassy, a marvellous actress, a dramatic dancer who feels the roles she portrays, with every fibre of her being, and a wonderful team player. I always looked forward to seeing her. She’s also great at comedy, not to mention her ENORMOUS stage presence. 🫶🏽🫶🏽🫶🏽
She will be greatly missed as a dancer, but she will pass on her great wealth of experience to other artists now🫶🏽
